title: BRIEF-Ambia Trading Group buys remaining 40 pct of advertising agency
text:
BRIEF-Ambia Trading Group buys remaining 40 pct of advertising agency 
Oct 19 Ambia Trading Group publ AB : 
* Says bought remaining 40 pct of advertising agency För närvarande reklam AB, also called Presens on Oct. 15, 2015 
* Paid 286,672 Swedish crowns ($2,294.48) for 40 percent of shares Source text: bit.ly/1NPX6Ji
